title: "About ShieldYour.Info"
date: 2019-04-26
---

ShieldYour.Info exists to help people who have decided to stop using privacy-intrusive tools, like Google and Facebook. There are other options for every service that the big tech companies offerâ€“from private file storage to encrypted messaging. One of ShieldYour.Info's biggest objectives is to spread awareness about these privacy-focused tools.

ShieldYour.Info is hosted on GitHub and runs on a Jekyll theme. Our site is free from Google Ads, Analytics and any Google gadgets or widgets. Our goal is not to rank highly on Google, but if you find our information useful, please pass it along! <em><strong>Thanks for reading and caring about privacy!</strong></em>
